
                          WELCOME TO AXE & FANG


Axe & Fang is currently running with the base world files. This includes
316 rooms, 200+ monsters and 150+ items at boot type.

*Note:  If you are new to Axe & Fang then type HELP NEWBIE before anything
        else.

*Death: When you die you are stripped naked and dropped in the town square
        of Tooth. Your corpse is now placed in the Temple of Tooth. This
        can be found by going west to the gate then north 1. To get your
        belongings back simply type GET ALL CORPSE.


*Areas: To get a list of the active areas in Axe & Fang to explore type
        HELP AREAS.

       ( Sysops may edit this file to post information to users. )
